Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.65,0:00:32.66,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}意料之外的危機 是神的饋贈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.76,0:00:33.51,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}無可奈何
